      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this superlative automotive specimen, preserved in a state that defies its tenure. This vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class, exhibiting a condition that can only be described as showroom-original. Every surface, mechanical component, and interior appointment has been maintained to an uncompromising standard, ensuring an experience indistinguishable from a new delivery. For the collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this offering stands as a definitive benchmark of quality and care.",
