    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019ve got something really special for you today. This car is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken incredible care of it, and it really shows in every detail. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically perfect and ready for its next adventure, you\u2019ve found it. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come see it in person!",
