    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly showroom-quality 2021 BMW M240i xDrive in Alpine White over Cognac Vernasca leather. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and shows zero signs of wear. The exterior paint is flawless, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating applied at delivery; there are no stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings to be found. The 18-inch M-Double-spoke wheels are free of any curb rash and are wrapped in the original Michelin Pilot Super Sport tires with ample tread remaining. Inside, the cabin still retains its new-car scent. The leather bolsters are firm and unmarked, the carbon fiber trim is scratch-free, and every electronic feature\u2014from the Harman Kardon surround sound to the heated steering wheel\u2014operates perfectly. Mechanically, the car is indistinguishable from new, with only 12,400 miles and a complete service history documented exclusively through BMW authorized centers. This sale includes both original key fobs, the factory window sticker, all owner\u2019s manuals, and a set of pristine all-weather floor mats. This is a collector-grade example for a buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 46900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
