    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen maintained to an uncompromising standard. This vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class, featuring an unblemished exterior and a cabin that retains its original showroom integrity. Rigorously inspected to ensure absolute mechanical excellence, this offering is reserved for the individual who demands a pristine driving experience and investment-grade quality.",
      "price": 46500.0,
