    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total dream! This beauty is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014I've babied it since day one, and it still has that fresh, new-car feel. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection inside and out. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one for you. Drop me a message, I'd love to show it to you!",
      "price": 43900.0,
