    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a superlative example of the high-revving S65 V8 era, presenting in showroom-grade condition. The 4.0L naturally aspirated powerplant features individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS, delivering linear power delivery up to an 8,400 RPM redline. Mechanically optimized with documented preventative rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, the chassis retains exceptional lateral rigidity. The 6-speed manual transmission offers precise gate engagement, paired with a variable M differential lock for superior corner-exit traction. Finished in pristine Alpine White, the vehicle exhibits zero bolster wear or interior delamination. This is a collector-grade specimen for the purist seeking unadulterated hydraulic steering feedback and atmospheric induction.",
